Subject: FSAM - Input Table is Version 2. Expected Version 1
Description: When executing the File System Action Module it fails - complaining that the input table is version 2, expected version 1.
Solution_Comment__c:
Issue
When executing the File System Action Module it fails - complaining that the input table is version 2, expected version 1.

Cause
The Action Module service expects the exe and libraries to be installed in a certain location but are actually installed in a different location.

To Diagnose compare the "Path to Execute" of the Netwrix Enterprise Auditor File System Action Moldule Applet service to the actual installation path %sainstalldir%FileSystemAM

Resolution
1. Remove the Netwrix Enterprise Auditor File System Action Moldule Applet via the NEA Action Configuration or by executing sc delete StealthAUDITFSAM

2. Execute the configured action via NEA
